Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.48,0:00:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs16\bord1\shad1\fsp1\b0}它花了几千年才长到这么大{\r}\N{\fn宋体\fs16\bord1\shad1\fscx60\fscy58\b0\i1}It's taken thousands of years to reach this size.{\r}
